44 class GSIRateLawGammaT : public GSIRateLaw
45 {
46 public:
47  GSIRateLawGammaT(ARGS args)
48  : GSIRateLaw(args),
49  mv_react(args.s_reactants),
50  pos_T_trans(0),
51  idx_react(0)
52  {
53  assert(args.s_node_rate_law.tag() == "gamma_T");
54 
55  args.s_node_rate_law.getAttribute( "pre_exp", m_pre_exp,
56  "The pre-exponential coefficient for the reaction "
57  "should be provided with gamma as a function of temperature.");
58  args.s_node_rate_law.getAttribute( "T", m_activ_en,
59  "The activation energy for the reaction "
60  "should be provided with gamma as a function of temperature.");
61  }

65  ~GSIRateLawGammaT( ){ }

68 
69  double forwardReactionRateCoefficient(
70  const Eigen::VectorXd& v_rhoi, const Eigen::VectorXd& v_Twall) const
71  {
72  double Twall = v_Twall(pos_T_trans);
73 
74  const int set_state_with_rhoi_T = 1;
75  m_thermo.setState(
76  v_rhoi.data(), v_Twall.data(), set_state_with_rhoi_T);
77  double m_sp_thermal_speed = m_transport.speciesThermalSpeed(
78  mv_react[idx_react]);
79 
80  return m_sp_thermal_speed/4.
81  * m_pre_exp * std::exp(- m_activ_en/Twall)
82  / m_thermo.speciesMw(
83  mv_react[idx_react])*v_rhoi(mv_react[idx_react]);
84  }
85 
86 private:
87  const size_t pos_T_trans;
88  const size_t idx_react;
89 
90  double m_pre_exp;
91  double m_activ_en;
92 
93  const std::vector<int>& mv_react;
94 };
